metadata.description:
1000 passes bringing you endless utility
Each pass grants you a 1:1 free mint of future weekly art releases

Each pass will also grant you access to exclusive holders only raffles. Raffles will be used for bi-weekly releases, with each release being 150 in supply creating exclusivity

Bi-weekly raffle mints will not have a public mint phase creating further exclusivity in owning the art

Weekly releases will coincide with Bi-weekly releases meaning there will be two weeks out of the month with a double drop

At the end of each month collectors will be given the option to [REDACTED] to [REDACTED] creating even further exclusivity

What kind of art will the future releases be?
FULLY ANIMATED — HAND DRAWN — FKED UP CREATIONZ
metadata.name: Fked Up Art Pass #1
